parameters: I think you'll be fine, but let me explain just in case.

In battle, you can perform a direct \c[2]Attack\c[0] with
your staff, release light arrows by converting spiritual
power with \c[2]Staff Magic\c[0], and activate spiritual
power with chanting for defensive \c[2]Chanting Magic\c[0].

Also, when you need to recover spiritual power, you should
select \c[2]Special Actions\c[0].

Be careful not to drop your staff, as you won't be able to
use \c[2]Attack\c[0] or \c[2]Staff Magic\c[0] if you do.

Damn, this strength... she must be one of the
\c[2]Guardians\c[0]' \c[2]Magical Girls\c[0]!!

Shall we test out the \c[2]Anti-Magical Girl Equipment\c[0]
that was issued for experiments!

Kohane-chan! It looks like the enemy is about to make a
move!

Be very careful! If your hands are restrained, you won't be
able to use \c[2]Staff Magic\c[0], and if your mouth is
covered, you won't be able to use \c[2]Incantation
Magic\c[0]!
